After Distro install we need

Video server, compositor and drivers
	xorg, xinit, xf86-video -vesa, picom / compton

Common C libraries and package tools for compiling dwm 
	libxft, libx11, libxinerama
	make gcc bc pkg-config
 
For a minimalist system you will need to install fonts:
	terminus-font (others are optional)

Sound drivers:	
	alsa-utils

If you run a virtual machine you will also need:
	linux-headers and virtualbox-guest-utils
############################################################
For Wayland display manager

Install wayland and libraries
		Wayland,  wlroots
		
Install IPC, login daemon and fonts
	noto-fonts-ttf elogind dbus-elogind polkit-elogind mesa-dri

Start services
sudo ln -s /etc/sv/dbus /var/service
the same for elogind and polkit

Install a compositor and tools
	Sway = like i3
	Swaybg, swaybar, foot (terminal)
    River, Hyprland

sway may break the cursor
	in the file /etc/environment    add the following line
   WLR_NO_HARDWARE_CURSORS=1


